        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                <p>Copied by Ramsay in 1886, published <bibl><ptr target="ramsay1897"/> <citedRange unit="entry"><ref target="https://hdl.handle.net/2027/ien.35556032371965?urlappend=%3Bseq=235">434</ref></citedRange></bibl>, whence 
