                    <bibl><ptr target="igc"/> <citedRange unit="entry">311</citedRange></bibl>, 
                    on which <bibl><ptr target="robert1955"/> <citedRange unit="page">228-392</citedRange></bibl>;
                    from these <bibl><ptr target="christoph1966"/> <citedRange>11</citedRange></bibl>, 
                    discussed <bibl><ptr target="cameronCF"/> <citedRange unit="page">148</citedRange> and listed <citedRange unit="page">315</citedRange></bibl>, 
                    <bibl><ptr target="IChrGr"/> <citedRange unit="entry"><ref target="http://repository.edition-topoi.org/collection/ICG/object/1015">1015</ref></citedRange></bibl>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
               <ab><lb n="1"/><g ref="symbol.xml#crux"/> <w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w> <w lemma="θεός">θεὸϲ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">το͂ν</w> <w lemma="ἀρχάγγελος">ἀρχαγέλον</w> 
                    <lb n="2"/><w lemma="συμπράσσω">ϲύνπ<unclear>ρ</unclear>αξον</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τοὺϲ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῆ<supplied reason="lost">ϲ</supplied></w>
                    <lb n="3"/><w lemma="κώμη">κούμηϲ</w> <w lemma="ἐγώ">μου</w> <w lemma="πᾶς">πᾶϲην</w> 
                    <lb n="4"/> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <orgName ref="#green" nymRef="#Πράσινοι"><w lemma="πράσινος">Πραϲίνον</w> <w lemma="ὁ">το͂ν</w> <addName nymRef="ὀρθόδοξος"><supplied reason="lost">ὀρ</supplied> 
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>θωδόξον</addName></orgName> <g ref="symbol.xml#crux"/>

               </ab>
               
             </div> 
           
           <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#cameronCF"><p>God of the archangels, help all the inhabitants of my village, and the orthodox Greens.</p>
           </div>
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="de" source="#IChrGr"><p>Gott der Erzengel, hilf allen in meinem Dorf und von den Grünen, den Orthodoxen!</p>
           </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#cmr"><p>God of the archangels, help all the people of my village and of the orthodox Greens.</p>
            </div>
         
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ramsay pointed out that the right side was broken, and suggested that further letters might be missing. 
                </p>
                <p>It was Robert who identified the location.</p>
            </div>
            
